Notification to the EAGGF Committee
The EAGGF Committee shall be notified of:
(a) the content of the call for proposals before its publication;
(b) the specific information measures and annual work programmes which have been awarded a grant;
(c) the activities implemented on the Commission's initiative as provided for in Article 2(1)(c) of Regulation (EC) No 814/2000.
